02:10.631 --> 02:11.829
<i>♪ Steam power,</i>
<i>it's so super!</i>

02:11.831 --> 02:14.333
<i>♪ Welcome</i>
<i>to a brave new world!</i>
<i>My word!</i>

02:14.335 --> 02:16.702
